Introduction

Dohee is a Korean pop singer and actress. She debuted in 2012 as the lead vocalist of the girl group Tiny-G. Dohee made her acting debut in 2013 with the tvN drama "Reply 1994". When it was announced in 2015 that Tiny-G would be disbanding, she later transitioned into acting full-time.
